# cycles.sheet — every kind of unhappy cell, plus one healthy survivor.
# B2 -> B3 -> B4 -> B2 is a three-cell reference cycle; B5 merely *reads*
# a cycling cell, so the error propagates to it.
case,result
three-cell cycle a,=B3+1
three-cell cycle b,=B4*2
three-cell cycle c,=B2-3
reads the cycle,=B2+10
self reference,=B6
divide by zero,=10/0
words in math,=A1+1
unknown function,=frobnicate(7)
out-of-grid ref,=XYZ99+1
parse error,=1++2
still fine,=sum(1,2,3)*avg(2,4)
